rComments: Biased,lack of subject knowledge, knows how to finish three hours of lecture without explaining anything. Just praises herself without any reason.

I wish it were possible to rate in the negative.  I'd give her a negative 3... b/c her existence isn't completely valueless- teaches patience.  She was horrible.  Worst lectures ever. extremely disorganized.

She's extremely nice and makes time for her students. Willing to talk and help us with concerns, gives good and timely feedback. She's very fair, except when the department screws over her students. Take her classes!
